comments: My favorite professor I have had in college. She is the sweetest thing and cares so much about her students. Lots of lectures but she makes them engaging and funny. Really knows her stuff! Takes attendance at the beginning of the semester but was more lenient toward the end. I enjoyed her class so much that I am taking her again this semester.

comments: Professor Wise is a nice woman, but she is a horrible teacher. Her lectures made me want to die. They are so dull and lifeless. Shakespeare is already pretty dry, but somehow she finds a way to make it worse. I would never take her again. Her classes are mandatory which stinks because her lectures drag on and seem to never end. I regret this class!

comments: Professor Wise is the kindest lady you will ever meet, and I wish I could adopt her as my grandmother. I wasn\'t crazy about the content (Medieval Culture), but she is a passionate and hilarious lecturer who helped us relate to the culture by making it relevant. Adorable, passionate, and offers extensions and help in any way she can.
